<item>
            <title>[LU-8113] Remove obsolete meta packages from spec file</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8113</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should remove the obsolete meta packages, deps-sles and deps-rhel, from the lustre spec file.  That approach nine years old, and the code to enable those packages has been commented out the entire time.  It is just dead code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is not an approach that we will want to pursue in the future either.  It would be better to either have multiple spec files or to use distro-specific macros to make various requirements conditional to specific systems.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
